# Hash Module - Allocation-Free Hashing for Baremetal
#
# Provides FNV-1a and CRC32 hash functions suitable for bare-metal targets.
# No heap allocation. All computation is stack-based.
#
# Public API:
#   - use std.hash.{fnv1a_hash_bytes, fnv1a_hash_i64}
#   - use std.hash.{crc32_byte, crc32_bytes}

# All functions exported from mod.spl are automatically available.
